## Results
A total of 15 centres were included in this study; contributing a total of 584 patients. Table 1 shows centres included in the study. The mean (SD) of patients include was 54.3717728 (16.6520009). The number of patients contributed by each centre ranged from 19 to 106 patients. The patients were recruited from the following clinics: ENT 280 (47.9452055%); General Surgery 131 (22.4315068%), Joint thyroid 75 (12.8424658%); Medicine 59 (10.1027397%); Other 11 (1.8835616%).


